						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">No date.</hi></p>						

						<p>States in verses that <hi rend="bold">Virūpāksha, son of Harihara,</hi> grandson of Bukka, and the daughter's son (<hi rend="italic">dauhitra</hi>) of Rāmabhūpati constructed the <hi rend="italic">vimāna, gōpura</hi> and <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> to Chakrin, i.e., Chakkarattāḻvār and that he further made a gift of the village Pāchchil to the deity.</p>						

						</summary>
